OL,5,CSean Brown
OL,7,FA High Court judge has ordered the UK
OL,8,FGovernment to hold a public inquiry
OL,9,Finto the murder of GAA official Sean
OL,10,FBrown.
OL,12,FMr Justice Michael Humphreys said
OL,13,Fthere is "a clear and unambiguous
OL,14,Fobligation" on the State to carry out
OL,15,Fan investigation into Mr Brown's death.
