OL,3,CGovernment ordered to hold public
OL,4,Cinquiry into murder of GAA official
OL,5,CSean Brown
OL,7,FLawyers for Mrs Brown argued that
OL,8,Fthere is an obligation on the State to
OL,9,Fcarry out an effective investigation
OL,10,Finto the death of her husband under
OL,11,FArticle 2 of the European Convention
OL,12,Fon Human Rights (ECHR).
OL,14,FIn his judgment on Tuesday, Mr Justice
OL,15,FHumphreys told the court in Belfast:
OL,16,F"I've concluded that there is a clear
OL,17,Fand unambiguous obligation on the
OL,18,FState to carry out an Article 2
OL,19,Fcompliant investigation.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
