OL,7,FMr Brown, who was the chairman of
OL,8,FBellaghy Wolfe Tones GAA club, was
OL,9,Flocking the gates to the training
OL,10,Fground when he was ambushed by
OL,11,Floyalist paramilitaries.
OL,13,FHe was abducted, beaten and shot six
OL,14,Ftimes in the head. His body was found
OL,15,Fnext to a burning car.
OL,17,FSpeaking outside court, his daughter,
OL,18,FSiobhan Brown, said the family are
OL,19,F"delighted" with the court's decision.
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@KO]
