OL,3,CGovernment ordered to hold public
OL,4,Cinquiry into murder of GAA official
OL,5,CSean Brown
OL,7,F"It's great news for us as a family.
OL,8,FWe've waited 27 years for this.
OL,9,FUnfortunately, we have waited this
OL,10,Flength of time to be in this position.
OL,11,FWe are delighted he has made this
OL,12,Fdecision," she said.
OL,14,F"Two High Court judges have ruled that
OL,15,Fwe should have a public inquiry and we
OL,16,Fare entirely grateful for that
OL,17,Fdecision."
OL,19,FShe called on the Secretary of State
OL,20,Fto obey the ruling of the court.
