OL,4,Cinquiry into murder of GAA official
OL,5,CSean Brown
OL,7,F"Do the right thing and (do) not
OL,8,Fappeal this decision and for us to get
OL,9,Fthe justice we deserve for our
OL,10,Ffather," she added.
OL,12,FThe family's solicitor Niall Murphy
OL,13,Fsaid it is an "exceptional judgment".
OL,15,F"It's legal history in one sense
OL,16,Finsofar as it is the first time the
OL,17,FHigh Court has directed, by order of
OL,18,Fmandamus, that the Government convene
OL,19,Fa public inquiry," Mr Murphy said.
