OL,5,CSean Brown
OL,7,F"The reason the court took that
OL,8,Fexceptional step is because of the
OL,9,Fexceptional egregious actions of the
OL,10,Fpolice and thereafter the secretary of
OL,11,Fstate in the 27 years since.
OL,13,F"Had the organisations, which had
OL,14,Fresponsibility, did what they were
OL,15,Fcharged with, had they investigated
OL,16,Fthe case properly, had they pursued
OL,17,Fprosecutions and convictions, this
OL,18,Ffamily would not have to wait for 27
OL,19,Fyears.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
